- var pageTitle = 'Online Cinema'

doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    title= pageTitle
    style
        include css/style.css
        include styles/normilize.css
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css")
  body
    include modules/header

    section.section-banner
        img(src="image/banner_2.jpg", alt="Banner").section-banner__image
        .container
            .banner
              h1.banner__title Zack Snyder's Justice League
              .banner-info
                span.banner-info__year 2021
                span.banner-info__age 18+
                span.banner-info__time 4h 2min
                span.banner-info__rating 8.8
              p.banner__text  Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source.
              .banner-control
                button.banner-control__btn.banner-control__btn-main Watch
                button.banner-control__btn.banner-control__btn-more More information  
    include modules/footer